Package ch.unibe.iam.graph.drawing

Interface Summary
GraphLayouter Computes the layout of a graph in the plane---possibly in a dynamic way.
 

Class Summary
EdgeRep Stores data specific to the layout representation of a graph element.
GraphElementRep Stores data specific to the layout representation of a graph element.
GraphRenderer Defines a new panel for visualizing graphs.
GraphRendererSet This class represents a set of graph-renderers.
GraphRep Stores a graphical representation of a graph.
InfoBox Displays general information on the currently loaded graph.
LayoutSettings Displays layout settings.
MultiDimensionalScalingLayouter Layout based on multidimensional scaling.
MyVisualizer Basic visualizer of graphs.
NodeRep Stores data specific to the layout representation of a node element.
RelaxLayouter Dynamically computes the layout of a graph in the plane using a modified version of the Spring Embedder algorithm.
SimulatedAnnealingLayouter Computes the layout of a graph in the plane using simulated annealing.
SpringEmbedderLayouter Implements the layouting model of Eades, also known as the Spring Embedder.
TimeLayouter
